{"tid":1563672,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍灣德福廣場穿梭巴士衝上行人路　1人死亡16傷","createTime":"2019-09-12T13:14:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T10:25:39.000Z","uid":297045,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"19c2df0c3d250dd568bb88f0f0e6331986a58ed0","tid":1563672,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:14:21.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】有一輛穿梭巴士在九龍灣德福廣場衝上行人路，至少11人受傷，1人被困。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=362555\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362555&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=4e89352a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362555&h=0582a014\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=362555</a><br />\n<br />\n晚上近七時，一輛穿梭巴士於德福廣場公共運輸交匯處疑失控衝上行人路，消息指至少11人受傷，一名男子被困旅遊巴與欄杆之間，該名男子昏迷，送往聯合醫院，而旅遊巴司機受輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n【2017】一死16傷<br />\n<br />\n【1955】17人送院，分別14男3女，當中14人為旅遊巴乘客，3人為途人，包括被困男子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2019-09-12-19-52-02aQcpF753.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2019-09-12-19-52-02aQcpF753.jpg&h=6962c574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2019-09-12-19-52-14THOKtCGL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2019-09-12-19-52-14THOKtCGL.jpg&h=e26f64f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2019-09-12-19-52-25w8gAXukB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2019-09-12-19-52-25w8gAXukB.jpg&h=f724b555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2019-09-12-19-48-27388dJehv.jpg\" da